About this item

  • Washable volumising and lengthening mascara for sky high eyelashes, Buildable formula with nourishing bamboo extract and fibres for fuller and longer lashes, Suitable for all lashes
  • For limitless lengthening volume from every angle, Lightweight body without the weigh-down, Richly pigmented colour without flakes, Defining, curling and lash-multiplying effect
  • For best results: 1.) Curl lashes with an eyelash curler 2.) Apply an eyelash primer, 3.) Apply mascara from root to tip in zig-zag motion, Easily removed with soap and water or makeup remover
  • Bendable Flex Tower mascara brush flexibly reaches every lash for full lash coverage, Ophthalmologist tested, Suitable for sensitive eyes and contact lens wearers

Product description

Product Description

Sky High lash impact from every angle! Lash Sensational Sky High mascara delivers full volume and a limitless length look. Our unique Flex Tower mascara brush bends to volumise and extend every single lash from root to tip. Washable mascara formula infused with bamboo extract and fibers for long, full lashes that never get weighed down. Allergy tested. Ophthalmologist tested. Suitable for sensitive eyes and contact lens wearers. Removes easily.

From the manufacturer

Maybelline New York

Lash Sensational Sky High Mascara

Sky high lash impact from every angle

Take your lashes to the limit with this lengthening and volumising mascara! The rich black formula is infused with bamboo extract and fibres for buildable, lash-lengthening coverage from root to tip. You're left with flake-free, full and voluminous lashes that won't lose their curl or get weighed down.

The unique Flex Tower brush bends easily for precise and flexible application, volumising each and every lash with each stroke.

Is the wand curved?

This mascara has a straight brush that bends to volumize and extend every single lash from root to tip.

When removing the mascara, is it flaky?

This long lasting mascara delivers full volume and limitless length. The mascara formula delivers long, full & lightweight lashes that don't flake or smudge.

Is this mascara OK for sensitive eyes?

This mascara is allergy and ophthalmologist tested. Suitable for sensitive eyes and contact lens wearers.

Is this good for thin eyelashes?

Our easy to use applicator works well on thin and thick lashes.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings, help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.

Amazon Customer
5 Stars
LOVEEEEEE COSMIC BLACK + PRIMER 😍🥰
This is to die for! It doesn’t smudge throughout the day, no flaking, nice formula, dramatic black. It’s just perfect. The only thing I will say is you have to let it dry between coats otherwise you may risk taking off bits of the one you last put on, but other than that it’s perfection! Also, remember to let your micellar water soak the mascara first when taking it off, give it time to do its thing, it’s not a tubing mascara as lots of people try to advertise it as (the formula acts as one, but it doesn’t come off like one). The addition of the primer is just *chefs kiss*. A BLACK primer at that, no more white or blue sticking out from under your mascara! I couldn’t recommend these products enough! I usually go for wired brushes, but I’m now quite fond of the silicone ones because of this mascara! If you’ve been debating whether to get this for as long as I did, do ittttt, it’s 100% worth it! 🤍✨

Her
5.0 out of 5 stars So nourishing!
Reviewed in the United Kingdom on 6 April 2024
Size Name: 7.2 mlColour Name: Cosmic BlackVerified Purchase
I only use mascaras that care for the lashes. With one coat/2 light coats they're still nice and soft even though the lift and hold is amazing. Wouldn't use too many coats as it's so effective, there's no need and they'd get clumpy with this formula. The brush is not my favourite to prevent this (perfect for lifting and bendy in a good way!) but can go in with a spoolie. Volume wise it's good if you haven't got many lashes otherwise it's length over volume. My lashes are curved yet it's like a lash lift with the addition of extra length and rich black pigment.
Came sealed and lovely seller!

4.0 out of 5 stars Mascara that stays on
Reviewed in the United Kingdom on 29 March 2024
Size Name: 7.7 ml (Pack of 1)Colour Name: PrimerVerified Purchase
Thought I was buying a product that I would use under my mascara in the hope it would stay on my eyelashes. This is a clumpy mascara that stays on. And then when my recent Chanel mascara finished and it was time to buy a new one, I did a bit more research. Sky High was constantly coming up as a recommendation by classy Eastern European bloggers and I decided to try it.

It came without a seal unfortunately, but when I opened it and checked for smudges around the entrance of the tube, there were none. So mascara wasn’t used.

Initially I didn’t like it, as it gave me slightly unnatural look. But after it dried out on the lashes and a bit of time passed by, I fell in love with it! mascara looks absolutely beautiful on my eyes. And the cost is so modest compared to what I am used to..

Sky High, although cheap in my books, doesn’t give me this black sleep, has a very easy application without staining the eyelid, and result is STUNNING! Loving it!
